column5: Where might be a launch around wasaga beach ??? Any that are public and I can launch at like 5 am??? Thanks
Across from the LCBO. I believe they charge for parking now.
What about the launch right at the mouth ot the Notty? I beleive it's Jenetta St.. It used to be a free launch
at 5am..  Just run down onto the beach, and launch there.  Right on the main drag..
